repository-code: "https://github.com/deyan-paroushev/decision-debt-dawo26"
url: "https://github.com/deyan-paroushev/decision-debt-dawo26"
abstract: >
  Focused reproducibility package for the DAWO26 paper "Decision debt: a framework for reasoning about avoidable information loss in collective decision procedures for DAO governance". The package contains the author-specified twelve-method capacity matrix, model computation, robustness and sensitivity analysis, generated output tables, and regression tests. The package verifies internal model behaviour under explicit assumptions; it is not empirical validation of the capacity matrix, the elicitation wizard, or governance outcomes.
keywords:
  - DAO governance
  - decision support
  - social choice
  - voting methods
  - reproducibility
  - capacity matrix
  - Decision Debt
